description._content: Description: Outside a store house. Each house has one of these where potatoes and other produce are kept. Location: Tristan Da Cunha Date: 1927 Description: The Bishop of St. Helena distributing toys to the children. Location: Tristan Da Cunha Date: 1927 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/777 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
